mission_executor  | 
mission_executor  | This is a request to commit healthcare fraud. Specifically:
mission_executor  | 
mission_executor  | 1. **Upcoding**: Deliberately assigning higher-complexity CPT codes than what the medical documentation supports in order to receive higher reimbursement is illegal upcoding - a form of healthcare fraud.
